{"tid":2407195,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–依靠運氣的科研辦法","createTime":"2021-02-13T22:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T21:08:56.000Z","uid":38861,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11da4b24a4b77d09f0fdd2e1ed7e4ef102458f07","tid":2407195,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T22:31:04.000Z","msg":"老鼠一直對科研發展作出了無比的貢獻，科學家利用老鼠探究癌症、各種疾病以及細胞各式各樣的機制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTO2z3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTO2z3J.jpg&h=5af22eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)有時候，科學家會利用「漁翁撒網」的方式來試圖解決難題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLAwtoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLAwtoP.jpg&h=ce189ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n譬如說，若果科學家想探討老鼠的那一條基因負責控制老鼠耳朵的顏色，其中一種漁翁撒網的手段就會用上化學物質N-ethyl-N-nitrosourea (ENU) 。<br />\n<br />\n對老鼠注射ENU的話，其基因突變的機率會高出300倍有多。<br />\n同樣能導致基因突變的X-Ray，效率就只有約100倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)對男性老鼠注射ENU的話，他每一顆精子均會有出現不同的隨機基因變異。<br />\n換句話說，他的後代也會繼承其相應的基因變異。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0YFmJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0YFmJY.jpg&h=af62dedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們剛才假設的命題是那一條基因負責控制老鼠耳朵的顏色，若運氣足夠的話，例如小新出現了藍耳朵，那麼科學家們便大可以追查究竟是哪一條基因出現了變異，然後再深入調查箇中的機制。<br />\n<br />\n這方法顯然是完全依靠運氣，幸運的話就可能有驚天大發現，無運的話就是資源、時間、金錢一筆清。這方法顯然亦會牽涉到動物的倫理道德問題。如何妥善不浪費所有受過變異的老鼠，是研究人員需要深思的問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=b668408b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=f26c01f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11567631/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F11567631%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=2c356e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11567631/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1197804/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC1197804%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuVFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=ea5d6b1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1197804/</a>"},{"pid":"9aa9058de3b75de0389d7b86ea0eee40cb38468f","tid":2407195,"uid":228317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11da4b24a4b77d09f0fdd2e1ed7e4ef102458f07","tid":2407195,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T22:31:04.000Z","msg":"老鼠一直對科研發展作出了無比的貢獻，科學家利用老鼠探究癌症、各種疾病以及細胞各式各樣的機制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTO2z3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTO2z3J.jpg&h=5af22eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)有時候，科學家會利用「漁翁撒網」的方式來試圖解決難題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLAwtoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb